@@pMAGE@@W

Mages are arcanists who study the raw architecture of power. Where others pray,
bargain, or brawl, a Mage bends elemental law through discipline, theory, and
precision.

@@pPassive class abilities@@W
  * @@wMage lifesteal chance scaling@@W: lifesteal trigger chance gains
    @@w+0.05% per Mage level@@W.
  * @@wMystical Potency@@W (unlocked at mortal level 20): increases your
    non-physical damage by @@w2% per point of Intelligence@@W.

@@pUnique Mage mechanics@@W
  * Prime mortal attribute is @@wIntelligence@@W.
  * Naturally synergizes with spellpower scaling, making Mage one of the best
    mortal foundations for sustained arcane damage builds.

@@pMage reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * Every @@w2 Mage reincarnations@@W (rounded up) increases max
    @@wIntelligence@@W by 1.
  * At @@w1+ Mage reincarnation@@W, @@wMystical Potency@@W is permanently
    unlocked for all future class paths.

See also: @@mreincarnate remort wizard sorcerer@@W
